~ start
if Inventory.get_focused_item() != null:
	Robin: Wow you are holding a {{Inventory.get_focused_item().display_name}}!
	Robin: How... did you know how to make that?
else:
	Robin: Hello, it's {{DaytimeClock.get_day_of_week_string()}}...[wait]\nHow are you?
	Fey: Hi!
	Robin: You have {{Global.money}}$
	if Global.money_today > 0:
		Robin: You made some money today, that is great!
	else:
		Robin: [speed=0.8]this is ok bu[wait=0.2] [next]
		Fey: Ok got to go bye!
=> END